---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to Speed Up a Slow Computer in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>Is your computer feeling sluggish? Here are the most common causes and effective fixes you can try before buying new hardware.</p>

            <h2>Quick fixes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Clean up temporary files and bloatware</li>
                <li>Check for malware</li>
                <li>Upgrade to an SSD if you're still on a hard drive (this is likely the BIGGEST performance increase you can get!)</li>
                <li>Update drivers and Windows</li>
                <li>Limit how many programs that turn on when the computer boots. You can always start the program if you need it!</li>
                <li>Complete the backlog of windows updates</li>
                <li>Restart the computer!! This fixes SO many problems!</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>When It's Time for Professional Help</h2>
            <p>If the above doesn't help, a full diagnostic and optimization from RigRescue can make a big difference — often remotely.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Book a Performance Tune-Up
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
